<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>病理数据平台</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="app portal-app">
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-brand">
      <div class="nav-logo">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 002 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0022 16z"/><polyline points="7.5 4.21 12 6.81 16.5 4.21"/><polyline points="7.5 19.79 7.5 14.6 3 12"/><polyline points="21 12 16.5 14.6 16.5 19.79"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <span>病理数据平台</span>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="portal-main">
    <header class="portal-hero">
      <h1>选择分析模块</h1>
      <p class="portal-hero-desc">两项独立流程：科室运营多维报告与工作报表柱状图可视化。各司其职，互不混用表格模板。</p>
    </header>

    <div class="portal-grid">
      <a href="/ops" class="portal-card">
        <div class="portal-thumb portal-thumb--ops" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="portal-mini-stage">
            <div class="portal-mini-frame portal-mini-frame--ops">
              <div class="app portal-mini-app">
                <nav class="nav">
                  <div class="nav-brand">
                    <div class="nav-logo">
                      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 002 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0022 16z"/><polyline points="7.5 4.21 12 6.81 16.5 4.21"/><polyline points="7.5 19.79 7.5 14.6 3 12"/><polyline points="21 12 16.5 14.6 16.5 19.79"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span>科室运营分析</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="nav-links">
                    <span class="nav-link portal-mini-muted">首页</span>
                    <span class="nav-link portal-mini-muted">工作报表</span>
                    <span class="nav-link portal-mini-muted">下载模板</span>
                  </div>
                </nav>
                <section class="hero">
                  <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1>科室月度运营<br>数据分析平台</h1>
                    <p class="hero-sub">上传 Excel 运营数据…</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="hero-visual">
                    <div class="hero-card hc-1"><span>支收比</span><strong>69%</strong></div>
                    <div class="hero-card hc-2"><span>门诊量</span><strong>+12%</strong></div>
                    <div class="hero-card hc-3"><span>满意度</span><strong>#3</strong></div>
                  </div>
                </section>
                <section class="upload-section">
                  <div class="upload-form">
                    <div class="upload-zone portal-mini-upload">
                      <div class="upload-icon">
                        <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
                      </div>
                      <p class="upload-text">拖拽 Excel 文件到此处</p>
                      <p class="upload-hint">或点击选择 · .xlsx · 最大 20MB</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="btn btn-primary btn-lg portal-mini-btn"><span>开始分析</span></span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="portal-mini-stepstrip">
                    <span class="portal-mini-sn">1 下载模板</span>
                    <span class="portal-mini-sa">→</span>
                    <span class="portal-mini-sn">2 填写数据</span>
                    <span class="portal-mini-sa">→</span>
                    <span class="portal-mini-sn">3 上传</span>
                    <span class="portal-mini-sa">→</span>
                    <span class="portal-mini-sn">4 导出</span>
                  </div>
                </section>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-card-body">
          <h2 class="portal-card-title">科室运营分析</h2>
          <p class="portal-card-desc">上传月度运营 Excel，生成经济运行、效率指标、全院排名与采购等综合报告；支持独立 HTML / PDF。</p>
          <span class="portal-card-cta">进入科室运营<span class="portal-card-arrow">→</span></span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/compare" class="portal-card">
        <div class="portal-thumb portal-thumb--compare" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg class="portal-compare-svg" viewBox="0 0 320 200" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="cmp-grad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#fbbf24" stop-opacity="0.25"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#fbbf24" stop-opacity="0.02"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <line x1="20" y1="160" x2="300" y2="160" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="1"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="120" x2="300" y2="120" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="300" y2="80" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/>
            <rect x="40" y="60" width="32" height="100" rx="3" fill="#3b82f6"/>
            <rect x="100" y="115" width="32" height="45" rx="3" fill="#3b82f6"/>
            <rect x="160" y="40" width="32" height="120" rx="3" fill="#3b82f6"/>
            <rect x="220" y="35" width="32" height="125" rx="3" fill="#3b82f6"/>
            <path d="M 56 70 Q 100 130 116 130 T 176 50 T 236 45" fill="none" stroke="#1e3a8a" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M 56 70 Q 100 130 116 130 T 176 50 T 236 45 L 236 160 L 56 160 Z" fill="url(#cmp-grad)" opacity="0.6"/>
            <circle cx="56" cy="70" r="4" fill="#1e3a8a"/>
            <circle cx="116" cy="130" r="4" fill="#1e3a8a"/>
            <circle cx="176" cy="50" r="4" fill="#1e3a8a"/>
            <circle cx="236" cy="45" r="4" fill="#1e3a8a"/>
            <text x="56" y="180" font-size="11" fill="#64748b" text-anchor="middle">1月</text>
            <text x="116" y="180" font-size="11" fill="#64748b" text-anchor="middle">2月</text>
            <text x="176" y="180" font-size="11" fill="#64748b" text-anchor="middle">3月</text>
            <text x="236" y="180" font-size="11" fill="#64748b" text-anchor="middle">4月</text>
            <text x="56" y="55" font-size="10" fill="#64748b" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="600">923万</text>
            <text x="116" y="115" font-size="10" fill="#dc2626" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700">-30.8%</text>
            <text x="176" y="35" font-size="10" fill="#16a34a" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700">+54.7%</text>
            <text x="236" y="30" font-size="10" fill="#16a34a" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700">+0.1%</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-card-body">
          <h2 class="portal-card-title">多月对比分析</h2>
          <p class="portal-card-desc">上传 2~24 个月度工作量 Excel，自动按月排序，生成 6 张迷你趋势图 + 5 张对比柱状图，让月份间变化一目了然。</p>
          <span class="portal-card-cta">进入多月对比<span class="portal-card-arrow">→</span></span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/workload" class="portal-card">
        <div class="portal-thumb portal-thumb--bars" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="portal-mini-stage">
            <div class="portal-mini-frame portal-mini-frame--workload">
              <div class="app portal-mini-app">
                <nav class="nav">
                  <div class="nav-brand">
                    <div class="nav-logo">
                      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 002 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0022 16z"/><polyline points="7.5 4.21 12 6.81 16.5 4.21"/><polyline points="7.5 19.79 7.5 14.6 3 12"/><polyline points="21 12 16.5 14.6 16.5 19.79"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span>月度工作报表</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="nav-links">
                    <span class="nav-link portal-mini-muted">平台首页</span>
                    <span class="nav-link portal-mini-muted">科室运营</span>
                    <span class="nav-link portal-mini-muted">下载模板</span>
                  </div>
                </nav>
                <section class="hero portal-mini-hero-wl">
                  <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1>工作量 / 收入 / 会诊<br>柱状图可视化</h1>
                    <p class="hero-sub">专用 Excel 三 Sheet，上传后生成对比柱状图…</p>
                  </div>
                </section>
                <section class="upload-section">
                  <div class="upload-form">
                    <div class="upload-zone portal-mini-upload">
                      <div class="upload-icon">
                        <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
                      </div>
                      <p class="upload-text">拖拽「月度工作报表」Excel 到此处</p>
                      <p class="upload-hint">或点击选择 · .xlsx · 最大 20MB</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="btn btn-primary btn-lg portal-mini-btn"><span>生成图表</span></span>
                  </div>
                </section>
                <div class="portal-mini-chart">
                  <div class="portal-mini-chart-cap">对比柱状图（示意）</div>
                  <div class="portal-mini-chart-bars">
                    <div class="portal-mini-chart-col">
                      <div class="portal-mini-chart-bar" style="height:46px;background:#3b82f6"></div>
                      <span>A</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="portal-mini-chart-col">
                      <div class="portal-mini-chart-bar" style="height:62px;background:#22c55e"></div>
                      <span>B</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="portal-mini-chart-col">
                      <div class="portal-mini-chart-bar" style="height:38px;background:#f59e0b"></div>
                      <span>C</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-card-body">
          <h2 class="portal-card-title">工作报表 · 柱状图</h2>
          <p class="portal-card-desc">使用工作报表专用模板（工作量、收入、会诊），上传后生成对比柱状图与导出选项。</p>
          <span class="portal-card-cta">进入工作报表<span class="portal-card-arrow">→</span></span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="app-footer">
    <p>病理数据平台 v2.1</p>
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
